  "faq": {
    "heading": "Know how EiffelFi works before you buy",
    "items": [
      {
        "question": "How quickly can I start investing?",
        "answer": "Sign up in about 2 minutes, complete verification, and start investing the same day. You’ll earn your first rent payment that day, and you can sell anytime."
      },
      {
        "question": "When do investors receive rent?",
        "answer": "Rent is distributed daily — every EiffelFi property pays into your account whenever it’s earning rent. Watch your balance grow each day, withdraw anytime, or compound it back into more property."
      },
      {
        "question": "Can I sell my ownership?",
        "answer": "Yes. List your shares on the EiffelFi marketplace and sell them to other investors instantly — no lockups, no waiting years for a fund exit. Instant liquidity is one of EiffelFi’s biggest advantages over traditional real estate."
      },
      {
        "question": "Does EiffelFi manage the properties?",
        "answer": "Investor-elected property managers handle day-to-day operations like leasing, maintenance, and tenant questions. A governance system lets owners vote on key property decisions, the same way a board would."
      },
      {
        "question": "What should I review before buying?",
        "answer": "Every EiffelFi property includes detailed financials, inspection reports, projected rental yield, local market data, and full ownership documents — everything a professional investor would want to see before committing capital."
      }
    ]
  },
